ep broken up, and the windows of heaven were opened."}, {:version=>"World English Bible", :text=>"In the six hundredth year of Noah's life, in the second month, on the seventeenth day of the month, on the same day all the fountains of the great deep were burst open, and the sky's windows were opened."}, {:version=>"Young's Literal Translation", :text=>" In the six hundredth year of the life of Noah, in the second month, in the seventeenth day of the month, in this day have been broken up all fountains of the great deep, and the net-work of the heavens hath been opened,"}]}